These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, mexican
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, fonseca
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, april
1. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the mexican is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | mexican    | colombian |
| Cigar         | fonseca | cain    |
| Birthday     | august     | april      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, water-polo
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, march
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda   |
| Sport   | water-polo | badminton  |
| Birthday     | march   | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, rose
2 different pets are kept: pony, horse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming
1. the person who growsrose is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Flower         | dahlia   | rose  |
| Pet   | horse | pony  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey   | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
City: nizza, miami
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, white
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, train
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who likes white##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| City          | nizza | miami |
| Color   | white   | blood-red   |
| Transport     | train       | ship      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-5::.
