.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, january
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, dancer
2 different games are played: poker, go
1. the person playing go is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
3. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Birthday    | january | october     |
| Job     | dancer | accountant |
| Game   | go | poker    |

 #################################

 
