.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, march
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, ivory
1. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | collecting |
| Birthday   | january     | march     |
| Color           | ivory          | amber     |

